# arvo-storage

Minimal L0 storage primitives for arvo. Hosts the only fielded
primitive types in the substrate: `Bits<N, S>` (the N-bit storage
primitive), the strategy markers (`Hot`, `Warm`, `Cold`, `Precise`),
and the platform-binding wrappers `Bool` and `USize`. Plus the typed
meta-bit newtypes (`IBits`, `FBits`, `Width`) used as `ConstParamTy_`
carriers for const-generic positions across the stack. `#![no_std]`,
no alloc.
